		<p class="desc">Arts Portals (#b000) are sites that lead to subpages or other sites covering a variety of art-related topics.</p>
		<p class="example">An example of this type of site is <a href="http://www.art-bridge.com/directory/abdir.htm">ArtBridge</a>.</p>
		<p class="subs">This type of site can contain subpages from categories <a href="ccowhelp.py?lang=en&cowc=bxxx&end=1">#b000-#bfff</a>.</p>
		<p class="similar">See <a href="ccowhelp.py?lang=en&cowc=b00x&end=1">Art Portals &amp; Search Engines</a> for similar categories.</p>
		<p class="similar">For serial publications of the arts, see <a href="ccowhelp.py?lang=en&cowc=03bx&end=1">Arts Periodicals</a>.</p>
